5:
Watch your footing! One wrong step
could mean your death.
14:
This isn't good... There's nowhere left
to run!
24: I've figured out the way. Follow me.
27:
Just now, I heard a voice...
Telling me to forge ahead.
43:
Do not waver, warriors! The hour of
our victory is close at hand!
45:
You will not fail! Not when the
Paragon of Hope—Estariel
herself—fights by your side!
53:
What is the meaning of this? Is the
same thing happening in other
squadrons as well?
59:
There's no doubt about it...
Champion, this is our world!
62:
The Doomsday Spear has pierced
through the sky?!
83:
I am most relieved to see you
unscathed, King of Man!
86:
I see. So this is your true form,
Champion.
89:
Unfortunately, it won't last much
longer.
98:
I was prepared for this. I... suppose 
I should consider myself fortunate 
I didn't perish in the process.
103:
Tell me, what exactly are we to do
without your strength?
107:
I can be of no further use—the
vessel of the Champion has been
spent. The power of the ancient
dragon, however, still remains.
110:
I would entrust you with this
power—will you see my mission
carried out to the end?
123:
Stella's right. You can't go around
talking like that, as if this is the end
for you. It's not.
126:
You're one of us. We're not doing
anything without you! That's how it's
always been, and that's how it's
going to stay!
138:
In that case, please allow me to see
the Mark.
141:
Rustamov... Until the very end, you
have served us valiantly. Allow us to
repay the favor.
145:
I can feel the power flowing through
me. It's... incredible!
157: Goddamn. That is one ugly monster.
161:
Adjudicus, does he still have the
same power as before? Is he
immortal?
166:
No. The link to the world of the dead
that sustained him has been
severed. Without a doubt.
169:
This being before us... is nothing but
a simple daemon. It won't
regenerate—all that's left is to put it
down.
174:
Then that is precisely what we must
do.
177:
To live to see a brighter tomorrow,
and to keep the promises we've
made... We have to do this!
182:
That's right! Alk, Nimbus! Don't let
your guard down!
186:
Let my guard down? Heh. Listen, you
do... whatever it is you do, and I'll
focus on kickin' daemon ass.
191: We can beat him! Now come on!
199:
Throw yourselves upon me,
weaklings.
Writhe helpless against the whole of
my loathing.
200:
Know this—only in the darkness shall
my people find salvation.
201:
Come... Stain your precious light
with the color of my blood!
